Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,确实不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:11.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「Glorious Angel号」这个名字有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.63,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有点bitch的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,而且听上去不太聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这叫华丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:21.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你有意见的话 就自己提个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.11,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那就…「Ātman号」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么鬼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.54,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,简单一点 叫「池袋快线」怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,有种就这的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是听起来很快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你有什么想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:37.51,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「Apogee」怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么G？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.55,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,远地点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:43.25,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,月球或卫星离地球最远的点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,听上去很时尚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是挺好吗 「远地点号」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:47.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,从今天开始你就是「远地爷爷」了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,原来静留你还喜欢星星和宇宙这些东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:56.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是我 是叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:00.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是叶香告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:01.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还是很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要说叶香喜欢什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,大概是绘本啊 软绵绵的东西啊 这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:09.79,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说起来 叶香为什么要去池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且还是一个人去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对 我一直都很好奇这点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:18.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,印象里叶香从来都没有独自去做什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:22.97,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对对 这样的叶香却一个人去了池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:24.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,很奇怪 不如说是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,稍微有点神秘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:27.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:30.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋还有什么去处吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:33.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还有就是书店、剧场、水族馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:35.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？她是会去这些地方的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.25,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,根本无法想象她会去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:42.89,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香是那种躲在人后不会出头的人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,她总是笑着跟在我们后面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:50.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉 我们其实不是很了解叶香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要啊抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.53,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,别说这么寂寞的话
