Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶 怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇刚刚呕吐了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,猫也经常会吐的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.04,0:03:56.79,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\bord0.601\pos(967.666,148.003)}第{\fs103.001}6{\fs}话    我说的话真的有这么过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但自从离开吾野后 它还是第一次吐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,它是不是吃了什么脏东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.55,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇要是出事了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:07.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,到池袋之后还得靠波奇找到叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,只有波奇能闻出叶香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所以 它必须得保持健康才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇今年多大了来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:20.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们还是小孩的时候就有波奇了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是说它现在十三四岁左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇这不完全是老头子了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,差劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我提到小雪奶奶年纪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你还对我生气让我不要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,和那时候不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,一样的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:37.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇要是死了的话…就死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶 你听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,多半没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你这样根本没有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.69,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你就不担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.22,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明明是静留你带波奇来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啥 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我可没强迫它来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是它自己跟着我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还在说这种话？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:03.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果要说我们现在在这里 都不是静留你强迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.27,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是我们自顾自跟过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,话是没说错 但是太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我之前应该和你说过了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.33,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 请告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香为什么去了池袋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.58,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你肯定知道些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么现在要问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.44,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在不能问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:23.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是不能问啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我就知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.07,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:41.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你对叶香说了或者做了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？叶香生气了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我根本无法想象叶香会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我其实真的搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,搞不懂是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.01,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你肯定做了什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她只说了「这样啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:57.99,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你说的宇宙 就是指这个宇宙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香你还会思考这些东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这种要怎么说来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是天文学吧！天文学！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:16.76,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我想从事的是 新的行星探测卫星、空间站的制导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.94,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,控制技术的开发和模拟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}要怎样才能成为从事这些工作的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.50,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.23,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,上大学 学习 发表论文…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.11,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,研究机关采用的话就去应募
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,应募？就这些吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.48,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,嗯 大概是这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:40.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然我也不是很懂 肯定很难吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.44,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.21,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,就算这样 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香你真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.71,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我才不厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哎呀 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,宇宙？卫星？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我从没想过做这样的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,根本想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:06:59.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,考虑得更现实一点怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.72,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,现实是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:04.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.47,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,字面意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.27,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟我们只是普通人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:13.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,像这种工作 不得是特别的人才能做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 我没有瞧不起你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但感觉 你在说的是很遥远的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.48,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,很遥远吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很遥远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从吾野到星星、宇宙和银河系？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说这种大话不会害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者说 更贴近现实一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.26,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,更普通一点不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们也只能成为普通人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说 别去考虑成为那些特别的人不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然叶香你会考虑这些是很好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但做不到的话会很痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说到底叶香你是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,当然 我也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们都不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.68,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,怎么指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你突然不说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说了什么奇怪的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.35,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.92,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,「这样啊」我只是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「这样啊」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:07.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你对我说的话有意见的话 直接说出来不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.85,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你这说法怎么这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很冷淡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我可没觉得自己说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.47,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.38,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留你原来是这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:24.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「这种人」是什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香你才是这种人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.45,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.26,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:34.61,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你道什么歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不管你了啊！叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.28,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我觉得是静留你的错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.89,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,突然被否定的话肯定会很低落很生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,尤其是自己的爱好被嘲笑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我知——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留她当然也是明白的啊 自己说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很过分吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说的话真的有这么过分吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟叶香也是因此才独自去了池袋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 为什么是池袋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 为什么是池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但叶香就是因为和你吵架才离开吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这个多半是事实吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.94,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算静留你没觉得自己说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要叶香因此受伤了 那就是你的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,静留你找叶香是要和她道歉的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香她不辞而别就不过分吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你们两个都有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.70,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,虽然这是你们俩的事 我不好插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但我对静留你瞒着我们到现在 很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 对啊 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这种「为什么不对我们说呢」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,负罪感？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,又不是我硬拉你们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.18,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.56,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是这样吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你觉得我们是擅自跟来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我以为是大家都想去池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你不是这么想的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:11.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我只是想去池袋 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.87,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,意思是你一个人去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也许吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啥？你这说的什么话？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,超级马后炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉 确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然还是我一个人比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说对彼此都是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要一个人去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:29.87,Default,Group,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等下啊 怎么这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.29,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,外面还是黑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子 拦一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留要跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.66,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,让彼此都冷静一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？就让她这么走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你觉得强迫她回来更好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.69,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.27,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,让头脑冷静下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.01,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你要去静留那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是？别走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:05.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇的话 肯定能对静留做点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.90,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.26,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是波奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去陪她们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然又要说我强迫你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.11,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.27,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是真的没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇你是自愿来的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我很冷淡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:35.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以说啦 抚子你怎么就能这么冷静呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果你只是想泄愤的话我是不会回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.05,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:49.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,大概有65%是泄愤 但有35%是真好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:50.60,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.04,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要去池袋只能沿着线路走对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而这线路又只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.62,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要沿着路走 绝对能遇到静留的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 原来是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你刚刚有一瞬间看着很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么？真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,来吃晚饭 调整心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:19.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这辆「远地点号」果然是静留的列车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,明明叫它Perigee也行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么G？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:23.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,近地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,地球和月球距离最远的点是远地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,最近的就是近地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留和叶香的距离？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 明明是要去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不取个近的名字 反而取个远的 感觉有点怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉是有点怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,再来一碗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啥？这么快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,耶！先到先得！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.69,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,会变成胖子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,别这么坏心眼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不想绕这么一大圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抄个近路！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,下一站是清濑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很快就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要尽可能早点到池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今天就停在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明早再出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:16.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果太快追上静留会很尴尬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,彼此都会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我会原谅静留的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟是朋友 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:29.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你的意思是 不原谅的叶香就不是朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.14,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:35.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吵架与和好都是朋友的一部分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是不和好的话关系会变淡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样也算朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就算一辈子都见不到彼此？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,别说了别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.14,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,睡前想难题会做噩梦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一个小时就该到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么爬了三个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,应该这么久吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:57.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不该的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,反应呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自言自语的话 我会害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么这么笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是不是回去比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:14.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我该回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:22.71,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么走来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,迷路的时候 不要下山而要上山 这是铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:49.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么回事 好怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂 波奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:55.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的假的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们哪来的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是清濑吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.23,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别小看吾野柔术啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.54,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.59,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,久违了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.39,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.51,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.68,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没见着她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,会不会是我们在哪看漏了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说不定已经跟她擦肩而过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但我们不是开得很慢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:23.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子 你说静留会不会离开了线路？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,如果是的话 她是从哪开始离开线路的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我就是在问你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可我也不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们是不是回头比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:32.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还是说继续往前？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但我们从早上开始都走这么远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子不是说 让彼此冷静一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是静留冷静下来之后想回来的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,回哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是 从哪里离开回哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真的有人离开之后还会回头吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说不定有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但那可是静留呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.53,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这么说来 我们甚至不知道静留会不会沿着线路走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 公路比线路还危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,也对…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但那可是静留呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,咦？不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:03.91,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,黑豹车队！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是猫哥他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.54,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,千仓静留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野高中二年级学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.72,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吾野高中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.73,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我是黑木美兔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.35,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,叫我黑木小姐就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:31.23,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,黑木…小姐 是僵尸…对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.13,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:37.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只是在想 为什么只有黑木小姐能说话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:43.33,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我会说话 那是因为我是僵尸的女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,僵尸的女王？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.58,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,开电车去池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.38,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,你们又在乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对了 猫哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你有没有什么情报给我们分享一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,关于池袋的最新情报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:57.49,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,说是最新 其实也已经是许久之前了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.96,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,而且还是我从别人那听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那也没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.44,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,唉 虽然吾野已经足够怪异了\N但池袋还要更胜一筹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:08.62,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,说是会被拉长变成广告牌\N或是被蒸成茶碗蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,根本听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.15,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:12.87,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:17.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个世界真的只剩下西武池袋线了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.15,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,我没有亲身调查过 所以不能下定论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.38,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,但也不能否定这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.87,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,特别是我在听了那些试图寻找其它线路的人的话之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.07,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你接下来还要到处转对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.21,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,嗯？没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果你在哪个村落上\N或是在旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:39.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,遇上静留的话 请转告她\N我们无论何时都会等着她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.14,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,这倒无妨…但我真能遇见她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 不是 这么说会显得你很靠不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.22,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,你们走了这么远 大概也意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.97,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,这个被7G所改变的世界\N变得无与伦比地辽阔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.74,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,想要遇上一个特定的人实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.48,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,虽说池袋是一处难关\N但这一带似乎也有着些许险恶的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.16,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,你们也尽早离开为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这里有什么危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.08,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,有僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.11,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你说的是那种尸体？复苏后的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们刚收到了迁徙僵尸的目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,迁徙僵尸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.92,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,别看僵尸长得吓人 其实它们纤弱得出奇
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.94,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,热了会腐烂\N冷了又会咔嚓一声断成两截
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.63,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H8E5232&\3c&HD6D4C1&\fs29.999\bord6.001\frz-20.74\pos(438,769.5)}强力除臭\N{\fs60.001\c&HC69844&\fnArial Black}芳香剂
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.94,0:19:21.20,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,下雨时会变得湿漉漉的\N但是过于干燥也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:27.05,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以我们总是在不断迁徙\N追寻着适宜的气候和土地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.11,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我是他们的罗盘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.07,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,身为女王 我有着指引他们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.52,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.87,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,是饿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.58,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,行 给她一根尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一根？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？根？ 根是指……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.70,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.18,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这种类似牛肉干的东西\N会塞牙所以我不是很想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.81,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.38,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:57.71,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.68,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好像不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那东西尝起来会是肉干的口味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.55,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.46,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我没吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:10.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.70,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我可是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.82,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,当然要吃特别的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.36,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(566,1)\fs45\fnVerdana\an7\c&HADBEB8&\pos(435,628.499)}八坂\N{\fs60.001\shad2.999}\h\h\h咸牛肉罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.56,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不能跟你们一块走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.43,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,毕竟我这边还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.03,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.19,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,要是遇上了僵尸 最好保持静止不动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:29.03,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,虽然那个对策也只是理论上可行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.04,Default,Group,0,0,0,,僵尸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是那种东西对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.14,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,会掉眼球 会发臭 会吸食脑髓 还会咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,被僵尸咬了就会变成僵尸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,多半会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是静留变成了僵尸 那该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.27,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,最近好像还有更聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,保留着生前人格的僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那它们不会袭击人类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,会袭击人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,猫哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,跟猫哥一块离开不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在追上去说不定还来得及！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.26,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是 那静留呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是静留真变成了僵尸\N我们跟猫哥待一块不是更好 也更安全吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:07.74,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你是觉得如果静留变成了僵尸\N她就不能跟我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.53,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就不是朋友了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然是朋友 但她变成僵尸了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就算她是僵尸 不也还是朋友吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:17.00,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就算她是僵尸 也还是朋友啊…是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:22.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果有一个女人跟坏男人交往 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:26.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果她说「只要他不赌博 不喝酒 就还是个好人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:31.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,难道大家不会劝她说\N「因为他会喝酒 所以他是坏人」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不就是这么一回事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.67,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不如说正好相反！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「虽然他这么不像样 但我还是喜欢他！」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「就算他这么任性 我也愿意原谅他！」这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是说「虽然她是这么个僵尸 但她还是朋友」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「虽然被静留说了那么过分的话 但她还是朋友！」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香会不会也是这么想的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她一定是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.33,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们得让静留找到叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯！
